@{u}Other BD Releases@{uu}:-

Currently there are only a few of many programs fully written and released,
here they are...

 @{fg highlight}256Colour 1.0@{fg text}               - Corrects the palette on 16+ colour
                               Workbench screens on an AGA amiga.

 @{fg highlight}AltNTab 1.0@{fg text}                 - Allows you to switch between windows
                               using a hotkey, just like Windows users

 @{fg highlight}ExtraScreen 1.2@{fg text}             - Opens a customizable Public Screen for
                               any programs that require it.  The
                               screen is then shut down when no
                               windows are open on it.

 @{fg highlight}StartE 1.0@{fg text}                  - Allows you to have up to 5 extra
                               startup-sequences available by holding
                               down the right mouse button during
                               booting.

To be released...

 @{fg highlight}Chord 1.0@{fg text}                   - A guitar chord database which shows how
                               to play certain chords.

 @{fg highlight}PhoneDial 1.0@{fg text}               - Use you modem to dial phone numbers
                               faster than you could, then drop the
                               carrier for you to continue the call.

 @{fg highlight}ExtraScreen 2.0@{fg text}             - A surprising update.

Plus many more that may or may not get finished :)
@endnode

